Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.47,0:00:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.03,0:01:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi won!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He won the Battle City Tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that Malik's dark half is gone,\N Mai and Bakura have returned to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi's won all the God Cards!\N This is incredible news!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And- what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The island's gonna explode?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba! There's a limit to being\N a sore loser, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And just as we were about to escape, the Battle Ship's engine stopped working!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell's gonna happen to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:02:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Alcatraz Burns"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto-{\i1}sama{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two! Stop being babies\N and get your asses out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we leave those two on the island,\N they're really gonna die, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yeah, my bad, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if they can't fix the engine in the\N Battle Ship, we're in hot water too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True. Either way, our best bet\N is to find Kaiba and have him\N deactivate the time switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's keep looking for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This island isn't that big.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sure to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I fought you on this tower and lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatred does not lead to true victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}had{\i0} to lose to me...\N so you can defeat your own madness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My friend lent me this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won through\N the power of my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The power of friendship, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, I put in the password!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Battle City was not only\N my struggle to become Duel King...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:04:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've also been fighting my grudge\N against Gozaburo, deep in my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was it my hatred that\N called him back from the dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's been an obstacle standing\N in my way almost my entire life...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good of you to come, Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been waiting to have a {\b0}nice{\b1}, {\b0}long{\b1} chat with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Humph. Don't make me {\b0}laugh{\b1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've got {\b0}plenty{\b1} of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we had a {\b0}hundred years{\b1}\N to sit and chat, I would only have\N one thing to say to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let us return to\N the Real World at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know, it's been some time\N since we used a game to settle\N one of our disputes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like the time I took you\N on as my adopted son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}SETO~!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gozaburo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will {\b0}not{\b1} be swallowed\N by the likes of {\b0}you{\b1}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But in the end, he was nothing\N more than a crazy ghost...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I already beat him until \Nthere was nothing left...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And now, as the new president\N of Kaiba Corporation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am about to sink all traces\N of him into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was I able to defeat those feelings\N inside of me, holding me back...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But what road\N should I walk {\b0}now{\b1}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That day a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I told Mokuba my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's finished, Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our Sand Park is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wow! That's awesome, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's my big brother for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen up, Mokuba!\N This is your big brother's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to build amusement parks \Nall around the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not parks made out of {\b0}sand{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\b0}Real{\b1} amusement parks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An amusement park where kids\N who don't have parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...like us kids at the orphanage...\N can play for free!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You mean we can all play together?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps, like these ruins on Alcatraz,\N my heart was buried in its own ruins...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lying somewhere under this rubble...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is the road to my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've only got a time limit\N of 13 minutes left!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Just 13 minutes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta stop the time switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Battle Ship's still not\N going anywhere, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto-{\i1}sama{\i0} and Mokuba-{\i1}sama{\i0} are\N the only ones who know how\N to stop the time switch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that bastard Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't think Kaiba-{\i0}kun{\i1}\N really plans to sink along with this\N island into the sea, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way he would.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba is the kind of man who only\N looks forward to the future and\N never looks back on the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm certain he has already found\N another way to escape this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to think that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's return to the Battle Ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's possible those two returned\N while we were out looking for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe they fixed the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otogi! Have they fixed the engine yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not looking good!\N It still isn't fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've only got ten minutes left...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! What the hell are they doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Can you fix the engine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just gonna {\i1}pulverize{\i0} it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the helicopter that came\N here to pick up Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're abandoning this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to explode!\N We have no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought the\N helicopter that came here for you\N would come in handy now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Less than one minute left!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30 seconds remain...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten seconds left!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detonate!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Duel Tower!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Battle Ship...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The island... is sinking...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Blue-Eyes White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT~!!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What'cha think?!\N Amazing, ain't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, it {\i1}is{\i0} amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys are genuine idiots...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guess, as long as they're safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey big brother,\N they're riding on a helicopter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Humph... Looks like they had some\N trouble with the Battle Ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OI, KAIBA!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}your{\i0} fault we almost went\N down with that island!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you have the nerve to {\i1}laugh{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}See, in order to build\N Kaiba Lands all over the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}me and my brother\N are goin' to America!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Build... Kaiba Lands around the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll invite you all\N one of these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, Kaiba... This is your new road...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi... Our battle is not over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To America! Depart!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba-{\i0}kun{\i1} has started\N a journey toward his new dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now... the other me's journey to \Nfind his memories has just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Time for us\N to return to Domino City!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba Land all over the world, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really looking\N forward to it, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really wish\N he could see it, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik has been freed from the curse\N of his dark half plaguing his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We three will take a new path... \Nand rebuild the Ishtar family\N in a shining future!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh... And "vessel" Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A day will soon come where\N you visit the land of Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that day comes, I hope you\N will see us again... as friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Egypt...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The place where\N the other Yugi must return...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... get the feeling\N there isn't much time left...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, we bid every single\N one of you farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to America.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After hearing about Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s plan\N to build Kaiba Land around the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided I can't\N waste any more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time I think of\N a new plan for my D.D.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He slipped her\N his cellphone number!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otogi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's leaving...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Everyone's got their own goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've all got \Ntheir own paths to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder... what my path...\N and goals are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find it eventually.\N I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right about that, Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're also leaving, Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've spent a little too much time\N roaming around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Battle City Tournament is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there's no reason for me\N to stay in this town any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:15:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see you go...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure he'll be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He really is a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's kind... and courageous...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even back in Duelist Kingdom, he fought for you as if his very life was at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why I'm certain the brother you see will be one who will never betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai-{\i0}san{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, I may have over-exaggerated a bit there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} the one\N who should be thanking {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were by my side the entire time I was \Nunconscious, weren't you, Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose to you \Nthe next time we meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. What the heck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least have the decency\N to say goodbye properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a lot of fun\N hanging around you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So much so that I lost track of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess your friendship was\N a little too bright for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right back at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You sure have grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Into a fine True Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if I'm being unfair to him...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I can't let things end here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every one of us are about\N to walk down a new road!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'm going to\N walk down {\b0}my{\b1} road!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, it's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where you headed\N this early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, right... Just a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a good chance\N to pay them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You should beat these guys up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way\N I'll do that to my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll be over for sure if I do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait for me, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... I can't leave without the puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}1, 2, 3...pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}, this is your card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now I can't take Red-Eyes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to become someone I can respect... a True Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, in this Battle City, I'll become one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, when I win this tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and when the time comes where I can call myself a True Duelist...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When that time comes, please fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll fight each other then, Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You taught me I wasn't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And you taught me courage... you're my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I {\b0}love{\b1} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop screwing around...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose, I'll never see Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...EVER AGAIN!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}WHAT!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gearfried... The...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:21:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will I have left {\i1}then{\i0}...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't die on me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to ask you\N what a {\i1}True{\i0} Duelist is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're early, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, I was working\N on my deck until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Battle City isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DUEL!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the Battle City Tournament has ended, everyone has begun walking their own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:22:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now that the other Yugi has obtained a clue on how to find his lost memories along with the three God Cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a new adventure is \Nright around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying that, when I think back on everything that happened with Yugi in Domino City,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it feels kind of nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what awaits us... is a farewell?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.02,0:22:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.64,0:22:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.35,0:22:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Sign"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.49,0:22:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.10,0:22:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.14,0:23:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.86,0:23:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
